{
  "page": "Sorcerer lord",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> God-Emperor</span><br />Chai</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nChai, sixty-ninth of the yellow emperors</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">God-Emperor</a></li><li>Sorcerer Lord</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Yellow_emperors\" title=\"Yellow emperors\">Yellow emperors</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>A <b>sorcerer lord</b> claims to be the sixty-ninth <a href=\"/index.php/Yellow_emperors\" title=\"Yellow emperors\">yellow</a> <a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">God-Emperor</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a>, despite the fact that the dynasty of the yellow emperors fell a thousand years ago. The <a href=\"/index.php/Sorcerer\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sorcerer\">sorcerer</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a> lives in exile, far to the east of of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Golden Empire\">Golden Empire</a>, in the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Carcosa\" title=\"Carcosa\">Carcosa</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Further_East\" title=\"Further East\">Further East</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. It is unknown whether he will prevail over <a href=\"/index.php/Bu_Gai\" title=\"Bu Gai\">Bu Gai</a>, the seventeenth <a href=\"/index.php/Azure_emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Azure emperor\">azure emperor</a>, enthroned in <a href=\"/index.php/Yin\" title=\"Yin\">Yin</a>, or another pretender, General <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a>, who claims to be the first of the <a href=\"/index.php/Orange_emperors\" title=\"Orange emperors\">orange emperors</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorcerer_lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The yellow emperor in Carcosa is a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to the book <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_King_in_Yellow\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The King in Yellow\">The King in Yellow</a></i> by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_W._Chambers\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Robert W. Chambers\">Robert W. Chambers</a>, and the fictional city of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carcosa\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Carcosa\">Carcosa</a>, both part of the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cthulhu_Mythos\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Cthulhu Mythos\">Cthulhu Mythos</a> of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H._P._Lovecraft\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:H. P. Lovecraft\">H. P. Lovecraft</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As exemplified by the names of the <a href=\"/index.php/Scarlet_emperors\" title=\"Scarlet emperors\">scarlet emperors</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Sea-green_emperors\" title=\"Sea-green emperors\">sea-green emperors</a>, and the fact that the fourth yellow emperor was <a href=\"/index.php/Chai_Duq\" title=\"Chai Duq\">Chai Duq</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> the family name of the sorcerer lord is \"Chai\".\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorcerer_lord&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_bones_and_beyond:_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Bones and Beyond: Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">SFBokhandeln. \"<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/OMvFNaqSWEo?t=36m18s\">George R R Martin visiting SF-Bokhandeln</a>\". YouTube, 2 July 2015.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-top: 5px solid #79DBFF;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pretender\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Pretender\">Titles in pretence</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Chai_Duq\" title=\"Chai Duq\">Chai Duq</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><small><b>—&#160;TITULAR&#160;—</b></small><br /><b><i> </i>69th<i> <a href=\"/index.php/Yellow_emperors\" title=\"Yellow emperors\">yellow emperor</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a> </i></b><br /><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">Reason for succession failure:</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">Throne contested by <a href=\"/index.php/Bu_Gai\" title=\"Bu Gai\">Bu Gai</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Incumbent</b>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404110448\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.247 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 713/1000000\nPreprocessor gener